Payment Options



You can pay at a location convenient to you. 

 
Customer Service Centers (Now accepting credit and debit card payments)

ALGIERS OFFICE – 4021 Behrman Highway, Suite J, located in the River Commons Shopping Center, New Orleans, LA 70114 

MID CITY OFFICE – 3400 Canal St., located on the corner of Canal St. and Jeff Davis Blvd., New Orleans, LA 70119
 
Quick Payment Centers (QPC) 

Please call 1-800-368-3749 (1-800-ENTERGY) for a list of authorized QPC locations in your area, or click here for a list. 

 

Customers should pay at an Entergy authorized Quick Payment Center to avoid disconnection of their utility service. Entergy authorized Quick Payment Centers will have a red and white sign with the Entergy logo and the words, "Authorized Payment Location."















































































