THE ENERGY STAR STORY






EPA's ENERGY STAR program stands alone as the
most successful voluntary energy efficiency
movement in history. To save energy and protect the
environment, the simple choice is ENERGY STAR.












 








WHY ENERGY STAR





Making smarter choices can
help us all use energy more
wisely. With ENERGY STAR,
all you have to do is look for
the blue label.





LEARN MORE






 







ABOUT EPA'S ENERGY STAR PROGRAM





From its beginning in 1992, the ENERGY STAR program has helped identify and promote energy efficiency in products, homes and buildings nationwide.





LEARN MORE






 




