Contact Us by Phone

Residential Customer Service - Monday through Friday 7:00 am to 7:00 pm
Business Customer Service - Monday through Friday 8:00 am to 5:00 pm
Report an outage or emergency - Representatives are available 24 hours a 
	day, 7 days a week.
Self-service options are available 24 X 7 through our automated system.

NOTE: To contact us by phone 
	you will need the telephone number or account number that is listed on your 
	Entergy account. Your account number can be found on your Entergy bill.
1-800-ENTERGY (1-800-368-3749)



Menu Options:


Option


Self-service options provided 24 X 7 by our automated phone 
			system:




If you're calling about a power outage, downed wire, streetlight 
			or  any other power related problem ...

1


Report power outage
Get power outage status
Set or change outage alert preference





To report a gas leak, gas odor, or any other gas problem ...

2


None, will transfer to an agent





For account information and other billing and payment matters ...

3


Get current balance, last payment information and past due 
				amount
Make a payment by phone (Quick Pay Center code and account 
				number provided)
Request more time to pay your bill





To start, stop or move service, or for new construction ...

4


Check the status of a service request including permit or 
				inspection requirements 





For all other matters...

5


None, will transfer to an agent




1-800-9OUTAGE (1-800-968-8243)

Report an outage or emergency - 
	Representatives are available 24 X 7




