Customer Care Centers 
Stop by one of our two conveniently located Customer Care Centers, 
        Mon-Fri, 8:00 a.m.-5:00 p.m.: 

West Bank Care Center (Algiers office): 4021 Behrman Hwy Suite J, located in the 
          River Commons Shopping Center.
East Bank Care Center (Canal office): 3400 Canal Street, located on the corner of 
          Canal Street and Jeff Davis Blvd.

Holidays 
Entergy New Orleans observes the following holidays: New Year's Day, 
        Mardi Gras Day, Memorial Day, Independence Day, Labor Day, Thanksgiving 
        Day, Christmas Eve, and Christmas Day. 


 


